opinion:
510 U.S. 961

In re Disbarment of Rios.
No. D-1324.

Supreme Court of United States.

November 8, 1993.

1

It is ordered that Raphael Rios, of Chicago, Ill., be suspended from the practice of law in this Court and that a rule issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
